    "Details": "The PRK-10 is a 15-ton ultralight built entirely around stealth and reconnaissance. A Chameleon Light Polarization Shield spans six critical slots across the entire frame for visual concealment while a Guardian ECM Suite handles sensor masking. Head-mounted TAG and Remote Sensor Dispenser enable artillery spotting and forward sensor networks. An ER Medium Laser handles light threats and a Flamer deters infantry. Three tons of Ferro-Fibrous armor and an XL Gyro keep mass minimal for maximum speed.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Advanced Optics</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.97</color></b>",
